>\n會考慮不同意見包括反對聲音<br />\n並獲得部分為數不少既泛民人士支持<br />\n代表：曾鈺成、田北俊、王維基、田北辰、曾俊華<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">中立偏建制</span><br />\n被戲稱為隱形建制派<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民生</strong></span>問題上可能會支持泛民主派<br />\n但政制問題上會偏向政府<br />\n代表政黨：專業動力、新思維、民主思路<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他扮獨立既建制派就未能列舉<br />\n希望大家係區議會 睇清楚政綱先投票 以免中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用您手上既選票 踢走晒上面呢堆撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望認真post有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e289bb62a73973529babb98954672cf6ebb71ca7","tid":1295761,"uid":82077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"8e57e38fbfb636727fd4a74b06c0fce059e75f81","tid":1295761,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e289bb62a73973529babb98954672cf6ebb71ca7","tid":1295761,"uid":82077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"我要驗傷"},{"pid":"9ab4e699cb334debad72aa3269b71f93c57e8cbc","tid":1295761,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be0a9170feb4456077c29d1743592129b546fd3","tid":1295761,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0943e5093b71b501020ddb1c7a5d29e4f6238147","tid":1295761,"uid":81424,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:38:24.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成係陰濕建制派"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"算係開明架喇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:09:24.000Z","msg":"佢啲語言藝術撚到好多人"},{"pid":"c0cc008ee0a33fbefd0047be4941c6808b284b7e","tid":1295761,"uid":82077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e57e38fbfb636727fd4a74b06c0fce059e75f81","tid":1295761,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e289bb62a73973529babb98954672cf6ebb71